00:01:57.630 --> 00:01:59.550
 nature and keeping up that as it is, or the nature of the mind, keeping up as it is with the

00:01:59.550 --> 00:02:00.000
 instructions.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:10.780
 That is what we are doing this, keeping up exactly, following the instructions, keeping up our

00:02:10.780 --> 00:02:15.000
 innate natures, exactly as it is.

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:24.000
 That is our "Vigalization". Now this "Vigalization", nature or character is one.

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:31.620
 Characterization of the "Vigalization" is, actually, ourself, ourself, we visualize meditating, our

00:02:31.620 --> 00:02:33.000
self as Buddha.

