 That Buddha, where it comes from? Where it comes from? This comes from the Buddha-nature, your

00:02:42.150 --> 00:02:44.000
 Buddha-nature.

00:02:44.000 --> 00:02:51.000
 Your Buddha-nature is what? They call it teaching, not just your, my Buddha-nature, your Buddha.

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:58.000
 But Buddha-nature is the embodiment of "blessfulness-emptiness".

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:09.450
 "Blessfulness-emptiness". "Blessfulness-emptiness", that "blessfulness" is instantly appeared form

00:03:09.450 --> 00:03:12.000
 of the deity.

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:19.160
 How that appeared? According to the instructions in the Dantara teaching taught, or sadhana taught.

00:03:19.160 --> 00:03:21.000
 That happened.

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:27.370
 So, reality, fundamentally, this deity, what we visualize, like Hayagirwa Vaidya, Vada is

00:03:27.370 --> 00:03:29.000
 definitely born and known.

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:38.000
 It is the great emptiness, great "blessfulness", union of the great "blessfulness", the emptiness.

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:44.800
 And that is the Buddha-nature, and that is what Hayagirwa in Vaidya Vada is, or the Buddhas we

00:03:44.800 --> 00:03:46.000
 visualize.

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:54.000
 How we develop that? We follow accordingly, in stockings, as the Buddha taught in the Dantara,

00:03:54.000 --> 00:04:00.000
 or sadhana taught by the Gurupin Masambha, according to the Buddha's teaching.

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:08.000
 Then we maintain that. So that is the essential meaning of the visualization.

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:15.000
 So visualization is not something that you make up that. It is actually happening.

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:20.000
 When we reach the Buddha-hook, when we become our Buddha-nature, we become the Buddha.

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:26.000
 According to sadhana, the Buddha-haktam is one of the highest capability practitioners,

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:32.450
 and his reach, the Buddha-haktam reach, the enlightenment of the Buddha-hood, up to three countless

00:04:32.450 --> 00:04:33.000
 eons.

